---
---
<section class="venue" id="venue">
  <div class="venue-inner">
    <div class="venue-header">
      <h2 class="display-headline venue-headline reveal">
        Behold<br /><em>Our Venue.</em>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="venue-layout">
      <!-- Image gallery -->
      <div class="venue-gallery">
        <div class="venue-gallery-wrap">
          <img src={import.meta.env.BASE_URL + "s1b.png"} alt="Samara Michael" class="venue-figure" />
        <div class="venue-img-main reveal-scale">
          <img src={import.meta.env.BASE_URL + "Hotel/hotel.jpg"} alt="Prince Regent Hotel" loading="lazy" />
    
        </div>
        <div class="venue-img-grid">
          <div class="venue-img-sm reveal-scale" style="transition-delay: 0.1s">
            <img src={import.meta.env.BASE_URL + "Hotel/h1.jpg"} alt="Hotel interior" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="venue-img-sm reveal-scale" style="transition-delay: 0.2s">
            <img src={import.meta.env.BASE_URL + "Hotel/h2.jpg"} alt="Hotel grounds" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="venue-img-sm reveal-scale" style="transition-delay: 0.3s">
            <img src={import.meta.env.BASE_URL + "Hotel/h3.jpg"} alt="Hotel function room" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="venue-img-sm reveal-scale" style="transition-delay: 0.4s">
            <img src={import.meta.env.BASE_URL + "Hotel/h4.jpg"} alt="Hotel exterior" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      

      <!-- Copy -->
      <div class="venue-copy">
        <div class="venue-address reveal">
          <p class="venue-address-text">
            London Chigwell<br />
            Prince Regent Hotel<br />
            Manor Rd, Woodford Green,<br />
            Chigwell IG8 8AE
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Prince+Regent+Hotel+Chigwell+IG8+8AE"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="venue-map-link"
          >
            Open in Maps →
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="body-lora venue-para reveal">
          A bootcamp that will reshape your financial life and set you on the path to freedom deserves
          to take place somewhere equally special — and this converted Georgian mansion fits the bill
          perfectly, with its picturesque scenery and elegant atmosphere.
        </p>

        <p class="body-lora venue-para reveal">
          The perfect setting for a comfortable, luxurious bootcamp experience — with stress-free
          parking right on arrival.
        </p>

        <div class="venue-highlight reveal">
          <span class="venue-highlight-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-handshake"></i></span>
          <div>
            <p class="venue-highlight-title">Business Networking Event</p>
            <p class="body-lora">
              Our Business Networking Event takes place on <strong>Saturday 2nd March</strong> at the same
              venue — where you'll be introduced to the kind of people who could change the trajectory
              of your business overnight.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="venue-perks reveal">
          <div class="venue-perk">
            <span class="venue-perk-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-square-parking"></i></span>
            <span>Free Parking On-Site</span>
          </div>
          <div class="venue-perk">
            <span class="venue-perk-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-utensils"></i></span>
            <span>Lunch & Refreshments Included</span>
          </div>
          <div class="venue-perk">
            <span class="venue-perk-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-hotel"></i></span>
            <span>Accommodation Available</span>
          </div>
          <div class="venue-perk">
            <span class="venue-perk-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-receipt"></i></span>
            <span>Business Expense — Keep Your Receipt!</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="venue-note reveal">
          <strong>Note:</strong> Book yourself a room from plenty of accommodation options so you
          don't miss out! Don't forget to keep your receipt — this is a business expense, so let your
          new Amazon FBA business foot the bill.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .venue {
    background: #1A1A1A;
    padding: 130px 0 110px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .venue::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--color-gold), transparent);
    opacity: 0.2;
  }

  .venue-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 60px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .venue-header {
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-bottom: 72px;
  }

  .venue-headline {
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 72px);
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.05;
  }

  .venue-headline em {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* Layout */
  .venue-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr;
    gap: 72px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  /* Gallery */
  .venue-gallery {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3px;
  }

  .venue-gallery-wrap {
    position: relative;
  }

  .venue-figure {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: -80px;
    width: 16rem;
    z-index: 2;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .venue-img-main {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 16/10;
  }

  .venue-img-main img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    transition: transform 0.6s ease;
  }

  .venue-img-main:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }

  .venue-img-label {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(26,26,26,0.75) 0%, transparent 100%);
    padding: 28px 20px 16px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .venue-img-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 3px;
  }

  .venue-img-sm {
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
  }

  .venue-img-sm img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
  }

  .venue-img-sm:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.06);
  }

  /* Copy column */
  .venue-copy {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .venue-address {
    border-left: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    padding: 20px 28px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  }

  .venue-address-tag {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #fff;
    opacity: 0.4;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .venue-address-text {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .venue-map-link {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .venue-map-link:hover { opacity: 0.75; }

  .venue-para {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 16px;
    opacity: 0.65;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .venue-highlight {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-gold);
    padding: 24px 28px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .venue-highlight-icon {
    font-size: 24px;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .venue-highlight-title {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .venue-highlight .body-lora {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 14px;
    opacity: 0.65;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .venue-highlight .body-lora strong {
    color: #fff;
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .venue-perks {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px 24px;
  }

  .venue-perk {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #fff;
    opacity: 0.65;
  }

  .venue-perk-icon {
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .venue-note {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #fff;
    opacity: 0.4;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.65;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    padding-top: 20px;
  }

  .venue-note strong {
    color: #fff;
    font-style: normal;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1000px) {
    .venue { padding: 72px 0 64px; }
    .venue-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
    .venue-inner { padding: 0 24px; }
    .venue-header { margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .venue-figure { left: 0; width: 11rem; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .venue-perks { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .venue-img-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
</style>
